pageTitle: Itinerary for Sunday, January 29, 2017 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Sunday, January 29, 2017:

Vancouver, British Columbia

10:30 a.m. The Prime Minister will participate in an Eye Dotting Ceremony at the Lunar New Year Parade.

Millennium Gate
26 W Pender Street
Vancouver, British Columbia

Notes for media:

  • Photo opportunity only
  • Media should arrive no later than 10:00 a.m.


11:00 a.m. The Prime Minister will participate in the Lunar New Year Parade.

Millennium Gate
26 W Pender Street
Vancouver, British-Columbia

Note for media:

  • Photo opportunity only


12:30 p.m. The Prime Minister will meet with Vancouver MPsâ€™ Youth Councils.

Closed to media


Note: all times local
